  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/f990baa85445bf60167e569e79ab38d1.avif?t=1741168318\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eastwind Adventures Chapter 1 </strong> is a storytelling and adventure game for all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/8063bebc0896f2321d4849f19ff90c76.avif?t=1741168318\" width=147 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Things are stirring in the lands of Eastwind. Great powers are awakening, some good, some evil, and all are drawn towards the mysterious islands in the east. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The strange, enchanted mists that covered these islands and kept them hidden, are withdrawing, and what is unveiled, will change the future of Eastwind forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young adventurer on a path to greatness, as a young sorceress who is just beginning to discover her power, and as an evil wizard with the ambition to become the most evil wizard in the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the first chapter of the Eastwind saga.  More are to come, and we will be looking to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >expand and improve the game with updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/68c81d0e687844351ec552616a0a1541.avif?t=1741168318\" width=221 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Chose your hero and fight the good fight in exciting battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Play out different stories with different protagonists. Some fighting for good, some for evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Explore the lands of Eastwind, and venture towards the enchanted islands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   that have been unveiled. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Forge a path to greatness, in wizardry or knighthood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/ea9b6df5ceb3620db6f25813bdfc5d8a.avif?t=1741168318\" width=175 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Join us on our quest, and we will have great adventures together!'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/f990baa85445bf60167e569e79ab38d1.avif?t=1741168318\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Eastwind Adventures Chapter 1 </strong> is a storytelling and adventure game for all ages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/8063bebc0896f2321d4849f19ff90c76.avif?t=1741168318\" width=147 height=79 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Things are stirring in the lands of Eastwind. Great powers are awakening, some good, some evil, and all are drawn towards the mysterious islands in the east. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The strange, enchanted mists that covered these islands and kept them hidden, are withdrawing, and what is unveiled, will change the future of Eastwind forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a young adventurer on a path to greatness, as a young sorceress who is just beginning to discover her power, and as an evil wizard with the ambition to become the most evil wizard in the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is the first chapter of the Eastwind saga.  More are to come, and we will be looking to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >expand and improve the game with updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/68c81d0e687844351ec552616a0a1541.avif?t=1741168318\" width=221 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Chose your hero and fight the good fight in exciting battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Play out different stories with different protagonists. Some fighting for good, some for evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*  Explore the lands of Eastwind, and venture towards the enchanted islands</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   that have been unveiled. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Forge a path to greatness, in wizardry or knighthood.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656870/extras/ea9b6df5ceb3620db6f25813bdfc5d8a.avif?t=1741168318\" width=175 height=93 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'Join us on our quest, and we will have great adventures together!'</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
